name: WeakAuras
description: WeakAuras is a powerful and flexible framework that allows the display of highly customizable graphics on World of Warcraft’s user interface to  indicate buffs, debuffs, and other relevant information. This add-on  was created to be a lightweight replacement for Power Auras but has since introduced more functionalities while remaining efficient and easy to use.
author: Stanzilla
